Class HDBOfficerController

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.controller.HDBOfficerController
All Implemented Interfaces:
canApplyFlat
public class HDBOfficerController extends Object implements canApplyFlat
Controller class for managing HDB Officer operations. Handles project applications, project registration statuses, and replying to project enquiries.
